  "detailed_description": "Bold Blade, the bitesize pixel art action RPG where your sword keeps getting <strong>bigger</strong>!<br>Pursuing the legend of a sword powerful enough to fell mountains, you journey to a remote island populated by demons.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/749110/extras/0c18ce048365af581c7749ec76c8f16c.avif?t=1517247874\" width=480 height=72 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/749110/extras/2ba559eb6720e840eca5c98c3515ef72.poster.avif?t=1517247874\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/749110/extras/2ba559eb6720e840eca5c98c3515ef72.webm?t=1517247874\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/749110/extras/2ba559eb6720e840eca5c98c3515ef72.mp4?t=1517247874\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Make your sword as huge as you want! What kind of sword is your favorite?<br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/749110/extras/5beeaea6f517cb883a85006657e9fc5e.poster.avif?t=1517247874\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/749110/extras/5beeaea6f517cb883a85006657e9fc5e.webm?t=1517247874\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/749110/extras/5beeaea6f517cb883a85006657e9fc5e.mp4?t=1517247874\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Balanced all-rounder<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/749110/extras/3c11d46d6b3cacc5406e7ef84533ebb1.poster.avif?t=1517247874\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/749110/extras/3c11d46d6b3cacc5406e7ef84533ebb1.webm?t=1517247874\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/749110/extras/3c11d46d6b3cacc5406e7ef84533ebb1.mp4?t=1517247874\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>The longest blade<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/749110/extras/c46663234b2c05f93ee173c49ca0a9cd.poster.avif?t=1517247874\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/749110/extras/c46663234b2c05f93ee173c49ca0a9cd.webm?t=1517247874\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/749110/extras/c46663234b2c05f93ee173c49ca0a9cd.mp4?t=1517247874\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Wider than the ocean<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/749110/extras/2c59f2bcd603902eecf3dd6123d7b3d2.poster.avif?t=1517247874\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/749110/extras/2c59f2bcd603902eecf3dd6123d7b3d2.webm?t=1517247874\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/749110/extras/2c59f2bcd603902eecf3dd6123d7b3d2.mp4?t=1517247874\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>If your sword alone isn't cutting it, purchase a variety of items to boost your passive abilities.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/74911